        <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies improvements to Customer Edge routers that help mitigate the problems that may arise when network configuration information becomes invalid without any explicit signaling of that condition to the local nodes.  This document updates RFC 7084.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
